    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable daily driver at a great price? This vehicle is in fair condition, showing some honest signs of its travels and typical wear, but it's still got plenty of spirit left for the road ahead! It\u2019s a solid choice for anyone seeking a functional, dependable ride that offers real value without the premium price tag.",
