    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for your next adventure? I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and she\u2019s in really great shape! She\u2019s been super dependable for me and still has so much life left to give. It\u2019s a smooth drive and looks fantastic parked in the driveway. Come take her for a spin\u2014I think you\u2019re going to love how she handles!",
