    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle offers a perfect balance of luxury and performance. The exterior finish retains a deep luster, showing only the minor, expected road wear consistent with careful ownership and garage storage. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the premium upholstery is supple and clean, the dashboard is free of UV damage or cracks, and every electronic feature\u2014from the dual-zone climate control to the high-fidelity sound system\u2014functions exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine runs smooth and quiet, benefiting from a rigorous preventative maintenance schedule and a documented service history. Recent work includes a fresh synthetic oil change, new cabin filters, and a comprehensive multi-point inspection that confirms its mechanical integrity. With its clean title, smoke-free interior, and a set of tires with excellent tread remaining, this car represents an exceptional value for a discerning buyer seeking a reliable, high-quality driving experience.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
